\par\pard\plain \fi288\sb240\sl480\slmult1\ql\ltrch\loch {\f1\fs24\b0\i0 Raefe watched her go and when she had, he let his mind open.}
\par\plain {\f1\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af1\hich\af1\dbch\af1\uc1\u8220\'93Were you able to get most of that?\u8221\'94 he asked.}
\par\plain {\f1\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af1\hich\af1\dbch\af1\uc1\u8220\'93Yes, all of it,\u8221\'94 Des said. \u8220\'93All of that was news to me.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f1\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af1\hich\af1\dbch\af1\uc1\u8220\'93Me, too. Except for their concern about Asia. I know the Rising Tide has been a thorn in their side. Many of the workers they depend on for food supplies from Asia are either secret Rising Tide or are close with them. And some of the processed food they buy actually comes from Rising Tide catches. So they are feeling more pressure as those sources either restrict what they\u8217\'92ll sell them or charge them more. Two things they don\u8217\'92t like. But the rest, no, that\u8217\'92s out of the blue. And worrying. Do you think it\u8217\'92s possible, what she was saying?\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f1\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af1\hich\af1\dbch\af1\uc1\u8220\'93Offhand, no. But then she claims they actually killed someone to demo it. At least we know what their goal is \hich\f1 \emdash \loch\f1  a weapon, not just surveillance or escaping surveillance.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f1\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af1\hich\af1\dbch\af1\uc1\u8220\'93And a weapon aimed just at empaths. They want to cut our heart out, so to speak. Where are you now?\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f1\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af1\hich\af1\dbch\af1\uc1\u8220\'93Southern France. There are some people here trying to resurrect fish farms along the Mediterranean. We\u8217\'92re working with them to see if we can improve on the old ways, lessen the environmental impact.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f1\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af1\hich\af1\dbch\af1\uc1\u8220\'93Can you take a break from that to look into this?\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f1\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af1\hich\af1\dbch\af1\uc1\u8220\'93Absolutely. There are plenty of Everywhere people here and it would be good for some of them to get more experience like this. Give me a couple of days and I\u8217\'92ll turn right to it.\u8221\'94}
